      <title>债券交易员大举押注美联储启动救援模式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bond-traders-bet-big-on-the-fed-launching-into-rescue-mode</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员纷纷押注美国经济即将放缓，美联储将需要开始大幅放松货币政策以避免经济衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bond-traders-bet-big-on-the-fed-launching-into-rescue-mode</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行维持鹰派立场，宽松周期落后于全球同行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/rba-set-for-hawkish-hold-trailing-global-peers-in-easing-cycle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚有望继续处于全球宽松周期的尾声，因为当地通胀和经济降温仍在加剧，这要求储备银行维持其基准利率在 12 年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/rba-set-for-hawkish-hold-trailing-global-peers-in-easing-cycle</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛经济学家将美国经济衰退风险“有限”上调至 25%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/goldman-economists-lift-limited-us-recession-risk-to-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团经济学家将未来一年美国经济衰退的可能性从 15% 提高到 25%，但他表示，即使失业率上升，也有几个理由不必担心经济衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/goldman-economists-lift-limited-us-recession-risk-to-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 17:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴菲特减持苹果股票 敦促投资者保持冷静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/apple-aapl-investors-urged-to-stay-calm-after-buffett-slashes-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有些人认为，伯克希尔哈撒韦公司减持苹果公司股份可能被解读为对这家 iPhone 制造商的增长前景缺乏信心。但华尔街的许多人都敦促投资者不要太在意这些消息，保持冷静。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/apple-aapl-investors-urged-to-stay-calm-after-buffett-slashes-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:34:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着市场情绪转好，加密货币在纽约再次蓬勃发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/crypto-is-booming-again-in-new-york-as-sentiment-turns-positive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币初创公司 Concrete 最近从旧金山湾区迁至纽约肉类加工区，这可能是“大苹果”数字资产复兴的萌芽的象征。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/crypto-is-booming-again-in-new-york-as-sentiment-turns-positive</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市正在轮动。问题是它下一步会走向何方</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/the-stock-market-is-rotating-the-question-is-where-it-goes-next</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美联储错过拯救美国经济的机会，上周股市出现剧烈抛售，结束了一场轮动交易，并可能开始了另一场轮动交易，投资者对股市下一步走势一片猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/the-stock-market-is-rotating-the-question-is-where-it-goes-next</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 13:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走势导致高盛和富达在新兴市场债券上产生分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/dollar-path-divides-goldman-fidelity-over-emerging-market-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团表示，新兴市场投资者应该青睐以美元计价的债券，而非以本币计价的债券。富达国际则持相反观点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/dollar-path-divides-goldman-fidelity-over-emerging-market-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国下令关闭移动互联网以平息抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bangladesh-orders-mobile-internet-shutdown-to-quell-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于周末再次爆发抗议活动导致 70 多人死亡，孟加拉国在三周内第二次加强了全国宵禁并下令关闭移动互联网服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bangladesh-orders-mobile-internet-shutdown-to-quell-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 08:40:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚最大油田减产 谴责政治讹诈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/libya-is-said-to-start-partial-shutdown-of-its-biggest-oil-field</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚受到国际社会承认的政府指责OPEC国家最大油田开始减产，并称这是“政治讹诈”。]]></description>
